{"tid":268250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本GPS衞星升空　定位誤差1米內","createTime":"2017-06-03T01:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T03:47:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f599637a4d72db3bce776f7235c130e87af8fd8b","tid":268250,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170602/large/rock02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170602%2Flarge%2Frock02.jpg&h=5e772080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本昨發射「引路2號」衞星（圖），為建日版全球定位系統（GPS）邁進一步，預計明年起當地定位誤差可收窄至1米內，準確度高於誤差最多10米的美國GPS系統。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">明年起投入服務</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n由宇宙航空研究開發機構（JAXA）及三菱電機共同開發的「引路2號」在當地時間昨晨9時17分，由鹿兒島種子島宇宙中心搭載H-IIA火箭升空，約半小時後進入日本上空的預定軌道。<br />\n<br />\n「引路2號」與2010年升空的1號機和計劃在年內發射的另外兩枚衞星合稱為「準天頂衞星系統」，衞星發送的訊號將與美國GPS系統兼容，明年起投入服務。4枚衞星進入軌道後，無論何時都會有至少一枚在日本上空飛行，以保證全國定位服務穩定。<br />\n<br />\n預計屆時日本系統在GPS輔助下，可將當地手機及汽車定位的誤差從目前的數米減少至1米以下，若使用專門接收設備，誤差範圍更可縮窄至最多6厘米。系統大大提高日本本土的定位精確度之餘，更可用於無人駕駛拖拉機和重型機械上。日本政府更計劃在2023年財政年度前將軌道上衞星增至7枚，屆時系統就可獨立運作。<br />\n<br />\n共同網/路透社"},{"pid":"c900194913a45c16ee7199c1b89c1843d1a15bbb","tid":268250,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"要痴住美國果套用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，姐係.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdbce057eab1f3770abf8fd16058a458b15fc28","tid":268250,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要痴住美國果套用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，姐係.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定係<br />\n因為美日同盟, 全部系統都盡量兼容<br />\n美軍同日本自衛隊既 DATALINK 係100%相通相容"},{"pid":"7b1bcde6a7bbe7685dd1410d13b6d89ef1551d73","tid":268250,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:00:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要痴住美國果套用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，姐係.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係支那己經玩完"},{"pid":"d17b04e9be9787dfbae72c1043e20ea1fe71ed62","tid":268250,"uid":18837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:20:02.000Z","msg":"誤所謂一米內都係要睇返當時環境<br />\n你除非身處大草原 唔係都唔會準"},{"pid":"33081587f5b1611a2aaf42202830256ef0651337","tid":268250,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>誤所謂一米內都係要睇返當時環境<br />\n你除非身處大草原 唔係都唔會準</blockquote><br />\n你有無試過係日本揸車用車載GPS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9a374ba2525faffb575ee9e62f4f6a78751cb5","tid":268250,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"可以做地震、火山爆發前兆嘅預報。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba8f97302fb7fca87780e5105878ac164ac43e","tid":268250,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"GPS有10米咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2169cbf6b5436a26c0381078dd091167d669b0","tid":268250,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得個名好重支那味"},{"pid":"ba52dd6df9a998328a2e4f12373b73b9e87b5192","tid":268250,"uid":47172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GPS有10米咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係羅 唔係話民用先有咁高誤差咩？"},{"pid":"cb067240956b440c9ca5d0b9b8dc7bb4f9d5e079","tid":268250,"uid":30421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T03:30:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人覺得個名好重支那味</blockquote><br />\n冇"},{